<p>Position: Malaysia Oil &amp; Gas EPC Business Research</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Location: Gangnam. Seoul</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Duration: 2019. 05. 07 ~ 2019. 06. 14 (6 weeks)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

