<p><b><u>Venture Capital Fund RaisingCampaign Intern Recruitment</u></b></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Ace I&amp;M Consulting,based in Seoul, is an financial services, business development, sales andmarketing boutique firm, currently engaged in providing an innovative sales andmarketing platform and series A capital injection services to a uniquefirst-to-market, globally leading IoT/Smart Factory supply chain management solutionprovider with a proven implementation track record to Samsung Electronics, HP,Amore Pacific, and many other Fortune 500 companies around the world.&nbsp;&nbsp;The target company is growing at a phenomenalrate and some of its pilot phase clients are $30B cosmetic company, $60Bconsumer home care company, leading auto OEMs and numerous Fortune 500companies based in the US and Europe.&nbsp;</p>

<p>We are in the midst ofexecuting series A round from globally leading VCs and looking for a passionate,intelligent, innovative finance major that would like to learn how to engageand support/execute the fund-raising process at the domestic and globallevel/scale.&nbsp;&nbsp;We are in need ofself-starting independent finance major student interns with the capacity tolearn and enjoy working at a small boutique firm which will offer an extremelyhands-on, in-depth work experience, often unavailable at large firms.&nbsp;&nbsp;Travelling and meeting local/global investorsin the US and Asia are essential part of the work and if likes to travel, itwould be an added benefit.</p>

<p align="left">&nbsp;</p>

