<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Marketing Research &ndash; Healthcare Team Intern</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Job Role:</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>As an intern at Ipsos Korea, you will have the valuable opportunity to experience how market research is conducted and delivered in the industry. You will be able to illuminate your notions of market research by being involved in utilizing cutting edge techniques and analyzing current market trends.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>What is involved?</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Translation, desk research, data entry, data checking, survey moderation, fieldwork suprervising, focus group notion, overseas support, etc.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; University graduate or soon to graduate</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Science / Health / Medicine Major or relevant experience in the healthcare industry</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Excellent English proficiency (written and spoken)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fluency in Korea (able to read, write, and analyze complex reports/studies)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Excellence MS Office skills</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Permission to work in Korea</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Desired Skills/Attributes</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Professional</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Proactive / Self-motivated</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Able to work effectively independently and in a team</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Able to work under pressure and meet deadlies</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Able to multi-task</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Required documents:</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>1. Ipsos Application Form (attached)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>2. English Resume &nbsp;(free format)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>3. Korean Resume (free format)</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>*Please combine the 3 documents and submit as a single Word file vial email</strong>: internapply@ipsos.kr</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Due date: 05.05</strong></p>

<p><br />
